# What are the strategic benefits of the capture of Soledar for the Wagner mercenary group?

## Summary
The capture of Soledar by Russian forces would be of strategic benefit to the Wagner mercenary group, a "shadow army" of thousands of former convicts and mercenaries fighting on behalf of Russia. <font color=#FF3399>[1]</font> It would allow them to turn their focus on nearby Bakhmut, which has been a target since the summer. <font color=#FF3399>[2]</font> Additionally, it would cut off the supply routes for Ukrainian troops in Bakhmut. <font color=#FF3399>[3]</font> Capturing Soledar would also be beneficial for Russian oligarch Yevgeny Prigozhin, the founder of Wagner Group, as it would allow him to criticize the Russian Defense Ministry's management of the Ukraine war. <font color=#FF3399>[4, 5]</font>

